[3441.543254, "o", "\u001b[H\u001bM       quently, one may use filenames with tildes in assignments\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[13;1H\r\u001b[K\u001b[7m page bash(1) line 2030/8010 26% (press h for help or q to quit)\u001b[27m\u001b[K"]
